headline: UnitedHealth Q3 Earnings Beat on Rising Commercial Membership
summary: UNH's Q3 earnings beat estimates on solid commercial membership gains and Optum Rx strength, though profits fall sharply on rising medical costs.

headline: How Investors May Respond To Cigna Group (CI) Launching a Rebate-Free Pharmacy Benefit Model
summary: Evernorth, the health services arm of The Cigna Group, recently announced the rollout of a rebate-free pharmacy benefit model that eliminates traditional drug rebates and introduces cost-plus reimbursement for pharmacies across its client base. This move marks a substantial change for the pharmacy benefit manager landscape, with the aim of increasing transparency, lowering prescription costs for consumers, and altering industry pricing dynamics.
